services.description:
First advertise, then expose
`id` is endpoint number `name` is `'scrd'` or `'sks\0'` for example. (4 char code)
struct app_info {
  uint64_t physical_addr;
  uint32_t virtual_base;
  uint32_t size;
  uint32_t entry;
  uint8_t name[12];
  uint8_t hash[16];
}

